# Secrets — never commit env files at any depth
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Windows NUL device artifacts + DB backups / wipe scratch
NUL
**/NUL
dev.db.backup*
*.empty-wipe-*
